## File Structure & Code Organization

### Core Components (src/components/)
- **`shared/MapLayout.tsx`**: Main UI orchestration, controls, welcome/logo modals; `mode` toggles behaviors
- **`shared/MapCore.tsx`**: Leaflet integration, pin rendering, interactions
- **`shared/MapControls.tsx`**: Search/help/GPS controls
- **`voting/VotingLocationModal.tsx`**: Voting modal with image and vote action
- **`proposal/ProposalMapPage.tsx`**: Proposal flow composition

### API Endpoints (src/app/api/)
- Proposal:
  - **`propose-point/route.ts`**: Accepts proposals, validates, creates Sanity docs
  - **`sanity-webhook/route.ts`**: Webhook handler, signature verification, D1 sync
  - **`geopoints/route.ts`**: Fetches approved pins (proposal map)
- Voting:
  - **`voting/geopoints/route.ts`**: Lists votable pins with `voteCount`
  - **`voting/vote/route.ts`**: Records a vote; returns `newVoteCount`; 409 on duplicate per fingerprint
  - **`voting/user-votes/route.ts`**: Returns voted pin IDs for a browser fingerprint

### Data Layer (src/lib/, src/types/)
- **`locationStore.ts`**: Frontend cache for proposal locations
- **`votingStore.ts`**: Voting state, fingerprinting, local single-vote enforcement, API calls
- **`browserFingerprint.ts`**: Fingerprint generation and hashing helpers
- **`locationImages.ts`**: Resolve location image URLs for voting modal
- **`types/geopoint.ts`**: All data structures, including `VotableLocation`, `VoteRequest/Response`
- **`webhookUtils.ts`**: HMAC signature verification utilities

### Configuration
- **`schema.sql`** (22 lines): D1 database schema with submitter fields
- **`wrangler.jsonc`** (93 lines): Cloudflare config, domain routing, D1/secrets bindings
- **`src/sanity/schemaTypes/geopoint.ts`** (144 lines): Sanity schema with workflow fields

