### Data Flow Modifications
1. Update Sanity schema: `src/sanity/schemaTypes/geopoint.ts`
2. Update D1 schema: `schema.sql`  
3. Update TypeScript: `src/types/geopoint.ts`
4. Update webhook: field mapping in `sanity-webhook/route.ts`
5. Update frontend: locationStore mapping
