## Security & Performance

### Security Measures
- **IP tracking**: Auto-logged for spam prevention
- **Webhook security**: HMAC signature verification required
- **Input validation**: Server-side validation all user inputs  
- **Content moderation**: All proposals require human approval
 - **Voting anti-fraud**:
   - Server: One vote per location per fingerprint (UNIQUE constraint), stores IP/UA/metadata
   - Client: Single total vote enforced via localStorage + fingerprint; shows persistent indicator

### Performance Optimizations
- **Map rendering**: SSR disabled, efficient marker management
- **Search**: 700ms debouncing, smart zoom calculation
- **Caching**: Client-side locationStore cache
- **Database**: Spatial indexing on (lat,lng), unique slug index

